value: I am L'Arachel, once the "beautiful princess of peerless beauty," but now you may refer to me as the "beautiful princess of fairylike beauty!"
Oh! I know it's hard to help oneself in the presence of such entrancing beauty, but look and don't touch, OK?
How considerate of you to pick out a new ensemble for me!
Look! Now I match Eirika and the others. Aren't we simply blooming with beauty?
Dozla! Rennac! What do you think of my new look, hm?
I'd give anything to see my mother and father...even if it were only in a dream.
With me by your side, you'll have the most pleasant dreams every night!
